      • getElementInfo

        public java.util.List<java.lang.String> getElementInfo(java.lang.String element)
        Finds information about an element and then returns a list containing that information.

        Format: atomic mass, molar mass, atomic number

        Parameters:
        element - a string containing the symbol for an element.
        Returns:
        A List<String> containing information about an element. See format above.

      • molarMass

        public final java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.Double> molarMass()
        Defines and returns a Map<String, Double> containing the atomic/molar masses of every element on the periodic table. Each element was added in order for the sake of convenience.
        Returns:
        A Map<String, Double> where the key is the atomic symbol, and the value is the atomic/molar mass.
        Since:
        1.0.3
